=head1 DESCRIPTION

Allow or deny permissions for an Active Directory group to enroll or
autoenroll certificates for a template.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AutoEnroll => Str

Allow or deny an Active Directory group from autoenrolling certificates
issued against a template. The Active Directory group must be allowed
to enroll to allow autoenrollment


=head2 Enroll => Str

Allow or deny an Active Directory group from enrolling certificates
issued against a template.



